track_notes: Parked at Deleo Sports Park and road mountain bike about a 1/4 mile to trailhead at Peony Dr. / Santiago Canyon Rd..  This is a 12 miles and 4,500 feet of climbing.  Be prepared for long day on the bike.  All gates were open to Santiago Peak on Dec. 7, 2023 so a vehicle could use this route also.
track_title: Santiago Peak via Indian Truck Trail from Corona
